# V&C`s Uno cards
This resource pack includes a set of cards for the board game Uno.
To use the resource pack, you will need an anvil.
When renamed, the texture is superimposed on the “paper”.

![Renaming process](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6095a6a536947b70a82962cf754f4fcb37a831b3.png)
**List of titles:**
- in quantity x2: blue_0, blue_1, blue_2, blue_3, blue_4, blue_5, blue_6, blue_7, blue_8, blue_9, blue_skip, blue_take_two, blue_vice_versa;
- in quantity x2: green_0, green_1, green_2, green_3, green_4, green_5, green_6, green_7, green_8, green_9, green_skip, green_take_two, green_vice_versa;
- in quantity x2: red_0, red_1, red_2, red_3, red_4, red_5, red_6, red_7, red_8, red_9, red_skip, red_take_two, red_vice_versa;
- in quantity x2: yellow_0, yellow_1, yellow_2, yellow_3, yellow_4, yellow_5, yellow_6, yellow_7, yellow_8, yellow_9, yellow_skip, yellow_take_two, yellow_vice versa;
- in quantity x8: order_a_color, order_a_color_and_get_four.



For the resource pack to work correctly, you must install modifications such as “CIT resewn”, “Entity Texture Features”, “Entity Model Features” or “Optifine”.
